  "text": "In this high-performing and selective school, the girls discussed how there was a pervasive atmosphere of being 'the top' with high academic expectations, redolent of a 'successful girl' subjectivity [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] : \"… in our school there's this whole big, I feel like there's a big atmosphere where the teachers are telling us we're really, really, really clever and we're like top…\" (Sabelle, focus group).",
